summary: First attempt at creating a female Bosmer.
descriptionHtml:
Personally I think this elf looks better with some sort of war paint. But I\'ll leave it to you to add in your preferred one (or just leave it).

Game saved at Helgen just before deciding whether to join Hadvar or Ralof.

Place file in C:\\Users\\-USERNAME-\\Documents\\My Games\\Skyrim\\Saves

Mods used:
Detailed Faces - http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=26
Smooth faces - http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=140
author: MrIllusion
